Daily Report 
<DATE1>  11 Apr 1994 </DATE1>

</HEADER>

<F P=100> North Korea </F>
<H3> <TI>   Spring Friendship Art Festival Opens </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Spring Friendship Art Festival Opens </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Art Festival Reviewed </H4>

<F P=102> SK1104070894 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0547 GMT 11 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK1104070894 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 11 (KCNA) -- The 12th April Spring 
Friendship Art Festival opened in Pyongyang and now is going on 
successfully. 
  Artistes and acrobats from many countries on the five 
continents and Korean artistes overseas put on stage colourful 
numbers winning high appreciation of the audience. 
  The festival places becoming more and more animated with 
each 
passing day are daily packed to capacity with working people in 
the city. 
  Festival flags and buntings are fluttering and marks, 
decorations, large posters and welcome slogans symbolic of the 
festival can be seen at theatres and halls where performances 
are given, including the Mansudae Art Theatre, the Pyongyang 
Grand Theatre and the Pyongyang International Cinema House, and 
on the streets of the city, adding to the festival atmosphere. 
  The festival which has developed into an authoritative and 
high-level grand art festival worldwide with the passage of time 
has been held traditionally from 1982 to celebrate the 15th of 
April, the birthday of the great leader President Kim Il-song. 
  Up until now, more than 700 art troupes and circus groups 
from almost all countries in the world have participated in the 
festival and the number of artistes and acrobats involved in it 
totaled several ten thousands. 
  Among them were many famous artistes including national and 
international concourse prize winners and people's artistes and 
merited artistes. 
  More than 100 famous artistes including international music, 
dance and circus concours and contest entrants are participating 
in the current festival. 
  During the festival, they will enjoy an impressive, pleasant 
time with sightseeing, amusement games, etc. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

<DOC>
<DOCNO> FBIS4-5563 </DOCNO>
