BFN 

  [Text] Tokyo, April 8 KYODO -- Japan's Overseas Economic 
Cooperation Fund (OECF) said Friday [8 April] it has signed an 
accord with Peru to furnish up to 2.24 billion yen in loans to 
the Latin American republic. 
  The untied loans will finance a project to reinforce Peru's 
