  [Text] Hanoi VNA April 12 -- Chairman of the National 
Assembly Nong Duc Manh received here yesterday afternoon a 
delegation of the Financial and Economic Committee of the 
Chinese National People's Congress led by its Vice Chairman Zeng 
Xianlin, on a friendship visit to Vietnam. 
  At the talks, Chairman Nong Duc Manh cordially noted that 
Vietnam and China are neighbours which have bound to each other 
centuries- old old friendly relations, and have many common 
features to share. They have stood side by side in their 
revolutionary struggles for national independence as well as in 
