<H3> <TI>   Top Leaders Hold `Secret' Meetings </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Top Leaders Hold `Secret' Meetings </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW1204145594 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME in English 1159 GMT 12 Apr 
94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> OW1204145594 </F>
<F P=104>  Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Ulaanbaatar, April 12 (OANA-MONTSAME) -- As is 
reported from well informed sources, yesterday there took place 
a secret meeting between the President of Mongolia P. Ochirbat, 
the chairman of the Parliament N. Bagabandi and the Prime 
Minister P. Jasray. They have exchanged opinions on the latest 
events in the political life of the country. 
  As is informed from those sources, today there has been 
scheduled a meeting of the Mongolian prime minister with the 
general secretary of the ruling Mongolian People's Revolutionary 
Party (MPRP), chairman of the Mongolian National Democratic 
Party on the initiative of the head of the government. However 
the meeting was not take place due to, as was formulated, 
illness of the MPRP leader. [sentence as received] 

