  [Text] Seoul, April 14 (YONHAP) -- South Korea has proposed 
signing a friendship treaty with China, North Korea's staunchest 
ally, during policy planning talks in Beijing, Foreign Ministry 
officials said Thursday. 
  Yi Chang-chun, assistant minister for policy planning, 
suggested that the two countries sign a friendship pact to lay a 
